[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: E, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 0, nRot: 1, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "5b28a9491e3e085cf8494d319bca3952176d3411848456d9ab034e4a7408ec92"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/michaels_unusual"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

Partner is 5-5 in \Ss and one of the Minor suits. Forget \Ss, you want him to bid the Minor. So you bid 2NT. Partner says 3\C.  

Partner only made a minimum bid, so you have no choice but to pass.}

